    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect blend of reliability and comfort for its next owner. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though it shows the honest character of light road use with a few minor stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, and all electronic features\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, having followed a strict service schedule with recent fluid flushes and a fresh set of premium tires. It drives straight and true, with a responsive engine and smooth gear transitions that make every journey a pleasure. This is a solid, dependable choice for someone who values a vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for many more miles of trouble-free driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
